These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, lemonade
1. Beverage:mirinda is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | mirinda |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
